│ - **File**: `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp`                              │
│ - **Lines**: 15891-15895                                                                   │
│                                                                                            │
│ ### 5. Conclusion                                                                          │
│                                                                                            │
│ The crash was caused by an incorrect assumption about the ordering of scalars in a         │
│ `SplitVectorize` `TreeEntry`. The `buildTree` function did not ensure that the order of    │
